Rollup Definitions for Record Rollups

Use the Record Rollup Definitions feature to streamline the aggregation of records from various objects or groups and to provide a consolidated view of your data.

Work More Intuitively with Record Rollup Definitions UI
Create record rollup definitions with just a few clicks by using an easy-to-use and intuitive UI. Use the record rollup definitions to aggregate records from multiple objects or groups according to your business requirements.
New Connect REST API Resource in Record Rollup Definitions
Learn more about the new resource available with Record Rollup Definitions.
title: Streamlining Data Aggregation with Salesforce
